90
00:04:55,099 --> 00:04:58,439
 I have something to report. Official Zhuang! 

91
00:04:58,439 --> 00:04:59,819
 Official Zhuang! 

92
00:04:59,819 --> 00:05:01,520
What is it?

93
00:05:06,620 --> 00:05:08,939
You'd better reflect on your actions.

94
00:05:16,110 --> 00:05:18,250
   

95
00:05:18,259 --> 00:05:19,859
What is it?

96
00:05:20,379 --> 00:05:24,080
Official Zhuang, Mu Zhuohua has returned.

97
00:05:24,080 --> 00:05:25,739
- Really? 
 - Yes.

98
00:05:25,739 --> 00:05:29,499
But you're heading to the capital next month for the triennial evaluations.

99
00:05:29,499 --> 00:05:32,380
- Well... 
 - I've taken care of the things there.

100
00:05:32,380 --> 00:05:37,320
But before I leave, I must settle things here first.

101
00:05:46,500 --> 00:05:49,899
You must deliver this to First Prince for me.

102
00:05:53,060 --> 00:05:54,860
Seventh Sister.

103
00:05:59,210 --> 00:06:01,410
   

104
00:06:02,300 --> 00:06:05,019
How fate has played tricks on us.

105
00:06:05,019 --> 00:06:08,099
I was the one eager to get married.

106
00:06:08,100 --> 00:06:12,139
Yet, because you got caught in the rain, and I lost my chance to get married.

107
00:06:12,139 --> 00:06:16,400
But unexpectedly, you ran away from marriage.

108
00:06:17,699 --> 00:06:20,119
And I ended up marrying the person I wanted.

109
00:06:20,119 --> 00:06:23,819
Speaking of which, I have to thank you, Seventh Sister.

110
00:06:27,980 --> 00:06:32,760
By the way, why didn't you go home since you've returned?

111
00:06:33,500 --> 00:06:35,980
How have you been lately?

112
00:06:38,219 --> 00:06:41,859
My life has been hard, of course.

113
00:06:41,859 --> 00:06:45,779
It's nothing like your high life.

114
00:06:53,620 --> 00:06:58,220
Eighth Sister, have you been doing well?

115
00:06:59,180 --> 00:07:01,100
Of course, I have.

116
00:07:01,100 --> 00:07:04,740
That's why I want to thank you, Seventh Sister.

117
00:07:04,740 --> 00:07:05,739
How about this?

118
00:07:05,740 --> 00:07:10,599
Instead of wine, I'll use this cup of tea to give you a toast.

119
00:07:39,019 --> 00:07:40,619
Seventh Sister?

120
00:07:46,420 --> 00:07:50,378
Why did you come back since you've run away from that marriage?

121
00:07:50,379 --> 00:07:51,898
It's fine even if you returned.

122
00:07:51,899 --> 00:07:54,779
But why did you let Butler Zhou see you?

123
00:07:58,779 --> 00:08:00,860
 You'd better listen to me. 

124
00:08:00,860 --> 00:08:02,619
 She's nothing more than an illegitimate daughter. 

125
00:08:02,620 --> 00:08:05,140
 Your mother said she was mine long ago. 

126
00:08:05,140 --> 00:08:07,939
 It's only reasonable and lawful for me to bring back my runaway concubine. 

127
00:08:07,939 --> 00:08:09,700
 What are you worrying about? 

128
00:08:09,700 --> 00:08:11,839
 But if you defy me, 

129
00:08:12,620 --> 00:08:14,599
 you know what I'll do to you. 

130
00:08:15,180 --> 00:08:17,280
 Do you hear me? 

131
00:08:17,280 --> 00:08:18,759
 Huh? 

132
00:08:26,160 --> 00:08:28,400
Just blame yourself for this.

133
00:08:52,660 --> 00:08:56,760
My beauty, you're finally in my hands.

134
00:08:58,219 --> 00:09:02,060
Do you know I've been looking for you everywhere?

135
00:09:07,459 --> 00:09:13,199
Official Zhuang, I've finally met you.

136
00:09:13,199 --> 00:09:14,698
Wait.

137
00:09:14,699 --> 00:09:15,779
What's going on here?

138
00:09:15,780 --> 00:09:17,919
You wanted to see me?

139
00:09:17,919 --> 00:09:20,080
Didn't you escape?

140
00:09:21,060 --> 00:09:25,240
I heard you were working under Lord Ding...

141
00:09:26,619 --> 00:09:29,859
when you were in the capital.

142
00:09:29,859 --> 00:09:31,999
Why did you come back?

143
00:09:34,180 --> 00:09:38,680
Official Zhuang, Lord Ding is a fickle person.

144
00:09:38,680 --> 00:09:41,459
How can he be a reliable long-term support?

145
00:09:41,459 --> 00:09:43,140
Besides,

146
00:09:44,020 --> 00:09:48,099
I didn't intend to escape the marriage back then.

147
00:09:48,099 --> 00:09:50,580
You didn't intend to escape the marriage?

148
00:09:51,180 --> 00:09:52,880
How so?

149
00:09:53,420 --> 00:09:54,578
Think about it, sir.

150
00:09:54,579 --> 00:09:58,580
If I did intend to escape, why would I return now?

151
00:09:59,300 --> 00:10:02,498
Actually, that day, I didn't intend to run away from the marriage.

152
00:10:02,499 --> 00:10:04,978
I was knocked unconscious and sent away.

153
00:10:04,979 --> 00:10:06,779
What happened?

154
00:10:08,900 --> 00:10:11,580
Sir, you don't know this.

155
00:10:11,580 --> 00:10:13,978
I'm only an illegitimate daughter of the Mu family.

156
00:10:13,979 --> 00:10:18,218
I never received any affection from the First Madam of the family and went through a lot of hardships.

157
00:10:18,260 --> 00:10:20,579
And you're the respected county magistrate.

158
00:10:20,579 --> 00:10:24,098
It's a blessing for me to be able to associate with you.

159
00:10:24,099 --> 00:10:26,299
How could I possibly want to run away from the marriage?

160
00:10:26,300 --> 00:10:29,140
I then gave the situation a thought.

161
00:10:29,140 --> 00:10:30,839
The marriage didn't go according to plan,

162
00:10:30,839 --> 00:10:33,260
and I was accused of escaping the marriage.

163
00:10:33,260 --> 00:10:36,700
So, I could only find a supporter in the capital.

164
00:10:36,700 --> 00:10:38,900
Who... Who did it?

165
00:10:38,900 --> 00:10:42,740
After giving it thought,

166
00:10:42,740 --> 00:10:45,939
Eighth Sister is likely behind it.

167
00:10:45,940 --> 00:10:47,240
Her?

168
00:10:49,219 --> 00:10:51,500
Why would she do that?

169
00:10:51,500 --> 00:10:56,558
You may not know, but that day, Eighth Sister invited me to the mountains to offer incense.

170
00:10:56,558 --> 00:10:59,919
Only then did I realize that she wanted to marry you.

171
00:10:59,919 --> 00:11:02,738
She thought I was dull and ordinary,

172
00:11:02,739 --> 00:11:06,179
which would make her appear more beautiful in comparison.

173
00:11:06,179 --> 00:11:12,219
But who knew that heavy rain would bring us together,

174
00:11:12,219 --> 00:11:15,459
