My Lord, why are you here?

256
00:18:26,219 --> 00:18:27,719
My Lord!

257
00:18:29,779 --> 00:18:33,379
Zhuang Wenfeng, you corrupted scum.

258
00:18:33,379 --> 00:18:35,480
Do you know who she is?

259
00:18:36,219 --> 00:18:39,099
She's Mu Zhuohua, a sixth-rank official of the Hanlin Academy

260
00:18:39,100 --> 00:18:42,240
and a court official appointed by His Majesty.

261
00:18:45,019 --> 00:18:47,819
You sure have a lot of nerve.

262
00:18:57,459 --> 00:18:59,299
How is His Lordship?

263
00:19:01,900 --> 00:19:04,658
The Yuanluo Flower and Snow Dust Pill in His Lordship's body

264
00:19:04,658 --> 00:19:06,379
have been maintaining a delicate balance.

265
00:19:06,380 --> 00:19:07,819
He shouldn't use force recklessly.

266
00:19:07,820 --> 00:19:09,698
He exerted his strength with force just now.

267
00:19:09,699 --> 00:19:11,679
Not only did it damage his meridians,

268
00:19:11,679 --> 00:19:14,739
but it also caused a struggle between these two energies.

269
00:19:14,739 --> 00:19:16,420
Do you have any solution?

270
00:19:18,420 --> 00:19:19,819
Go to the Mu Residence.

271
00:19:19,820 --> 00:19:21,179
Where's Zhijian?

272
00:19:21,180 --> 00:19:25,260
Zhijian will meet us after he reports our safety to the First Prince.

273
00:19:35,121 --> 00:19:39,978
   

274
00:19:39,979 --> 00:19:41,379
Who are you?

275
00:19:48,900 --> 00:19:51,158
- Why are you here? 
 - Greetings, Your Highness.

276
00:19:51,158 --> 00:19:53,078
I came to Jiangnan with Lord Ding on official duties.

277
00:19:53,078 --> 00:19:54,879
Uncle is also here?

278
00:19:54,879 --> 00:19:55,919
That's perfect.

279
00:19:55,919 --> 00:19:57,419
Follow me and rescue Mu Zhuohua.

280
00:19:57,420 --> 00:19:59,778
Your Highness, Official Mu is safe.

281
00:19:59,779 --> 00:20:01,779
She sent me to bring the news of her safety to you.

282
00:20:02,385 --> 00:20:04,798
However, His Lordship

283
00:20:04,798 --> 00:20:06,699
Uncle is injured?

284
00:20:08,219 --> 00:20:09,538
Where is he? Take me to him now.

285
00:20:09,539 --> 00:20:14,199
Your Highness, Official Mu has taken His Lordship to a relative's house for treatment.

286
00:20:14,199 --> 00:20:16,159
You don't need to worry.

287
00:20:16,159 --> 00:20:18,218
She also said the current situation is unstable.

288
00:20:18,219 --> 00:20:21,520
You need to stay at the county office to reassure the people.

289
00:20:24,539 --> 00:20:26,239
I understand.

290
00:20:26,239 --> 00:20:28,420
Take care of Uncle.

291
00:20:28,420 --> 00:20:30,980
I'll handle the disaster relief.

292
00:20:30,980 --> 00:20:32,787
Yes, Your Highness.

293
00:20:33,900 --> 00:20:36,439
Your Highness, we counted the grains in the granary

294
00:20:36,439 --> 00:20:38,419
and found that the quantity of relief grains doesn't match up.

295
00:20:38,420 --> 00:20:41,179
I'm afraid Zhuang Wenfeng has sold off most of it.

296
00:20:41,180 --> 00:20:43,719
How much longer can the remaining grain last?

297
00:20:43,719 --> 00:20:46,179
If we continue making congee with the same amount as before,

298
00:20:46,180 --> 00:20:48,500
it can only last for up to seven days.

299
00:20:51,200 --> 00:20:53,778
Transport the remaining relief grain to the congee stall.

300
00:20:53,779 --> 00:20:59,199
I'll issue an order to nearby counties to send a new batch of relief grain.

301
00:20:59,680 --> 00:21:01,939
The congee portion must be the same as the previous days.

302
00:21:01,940 --> 00:21:03,379
We mustn't deceive the people.

303
00:21:03,380 --> 00:21:04,880
Yes, Your Highness.

304
00:21:08,499 --> 00:21:09,759
Why are you still here?

305
00:21:09,759 --> 00:21:11,520
Go and take care of Uncle.

306
00:21:11,520 --> 00:21:15,639
Your Highness, I haven't finished my words.

307
00:21:15,639 --> 00:21:17,299
Then go on.

308
00:21:21,019 --> 00:21:22,158
Have you heard?

309
00:21:22,158 --> 00:21:24,859
County Magistrate Zhuang has been arrested by First Prince, who came from the capital.

310
00:21:24,859 --> 00:21:27,078
 It serves him right. That Zhuang has been overbearing for too long. 

311
00:21:27,078 --> 00:21:28,859
 It's about time he was caught. 

312
00:21:28,860 --> 00:21:30,899
 This is karma catching up to him. 

313
00:21:30,900 --> 00:21:32,600
 Indeed. 

314
00:21:34,860 --> 00:21:38,059
 Zhuang Wenfeng has caused the people to suffer. 

315
00:21:38,059 --> 00:21:40,419
 Yet, he's still safe to this day. 

316
00:21:40,419 --> 00:21:44,240
 The situation in Jiangnan is quite complicated. 

317
00:21:48,050 --> 00:21:52,000
   

318
00:22:01,779 --> 00:22:04,619
Now that County Magistrate Zhuang has been arrested,

319
00:22:05,380 --> 00:22:10,920
I wonder if all the business dealings we colluded in before will come to light.

320
00:22:11,900 --> 00:22:17,959
That depends on the relationship between you and County Magistrate Zhuang.

321
00:22:17,959 --> 00:22:19,760
Stop teasing me.

322
00:22:19,760 --> 00:22:21,439
Master! Madam!

323
00:22:24,480 --> 00:22:27,599
Master. Madam. Miss Seventh has returned.

324
00:22:29,040 --> 00:22:30,840
Qi?

325
00:22:32,879 --> 00:22:35,599
Didn't she marry County Magistrate Zhuang?

326
00:22:37,320 --> 00:22:40,380
Why is that darned lass back now?

327
00:22:41,639 --> 00:22:42,939
Master...

328
00:22:43,779 --> 00:22:48,399
Madam, wasn't it Miss Eighth who married County Magistrate Zhuang?

329
00:22:49,960 --> 00:22:51,960
Don't I know that?

330
00:22:54,697 --> 00:22:58,830
   

331
00:23:06,299 --> 00:23:07,698
Did you report it to First Prince?

332
00:23:07,699 --> 00:23:09,599
How's His Lordship?

333
00:23:13,019 --> 00:23:16,339
What's going on here? Why is this carriage in the courtyard?

334
00:23:16,339 --> 00:23:19,139
Miss Seventh... She has an official badge.

335
00:23:19,139 --> 00:23:23,040
Official badge? I have a belt!

336
00:23:27,700 --> 00:23:29,600
   

337
00:23:31,140 --> 00:23:34,000
Administrator of the Ministry of Rites?

338
00:23:38,480 --> 00:23:40,620
Official Mu.

339
00:23:41,539 --> 00:23:42,879
It's been a while.

340
00:23:42,879 --> 00:23:45,739
Old Master Mu, we meet again.

341
00:23:46,580 --> 00:23:49,979
Is First Prince in the carriage?

342
00:23:51,200 --> 00:23:54,559
His Highness didn't come. I have an urgent matter.

343
00:23:54,559 --> 00:23:57,200
Hope you can lend a chamber to me.

344
00:23:57,200 --> 00:23:59,979
Of course, it's not a problem. Please come inside.

345
00:23:59,979 --> 00:24:03,698
Qi, you know the way. Take your friend there.

346
00:24:03,698 --> 00:24:06,539
If you need anything, just let me know.

347
00:24:06,539 --> 00:24:08,359
Thank you, Mother.

348
00:24:14,999 --> 00:24:17,619
My dear, what did you call her?

349
00:24:17,620 --> 00:24:19,799
Qi?

350
00:24:20,820 --> 00:24:23,859
Your daughter, Qi.

351
00:24:23,859 --> 00:24:26,498
- She's my daughter, Qi? 
 - Yes.

352
00:24:26,498 --> 00:24:30,100
My dear, is she really my daughter?

353
00:25:01,799 --> 00:25:04,019
His Lordship's pulse has stabilized for now.

354
00:25:04,019 --> 00:25:06,179
Stay here and take care of His Lordship. I'll be back soon.

355
00:25:06,179 --> 00:25:08,439
- Is His Lordship... 
 - Is His Lordship safe now?

356
00:25:10,319 --> 00:25:12,519
I won't let anything happen to him.

357
00:25:14,180 --> 00:25:17,978
 My Lord,  you must survive. 

358
00:25:17,979 --> 00:25:23,200
 You're the pillar of the Cangwu Army, the unyielding rock of Southern Chen 

359
00:25:23,200 --> 00:25:27,620
 As long as you're here, the spirit of the Cangwu Army will never fade! 

360
00:25:27,620 --> 00:25:32,079
 - My Lord, you must survive. 
 - Live on! 

361
00:25:38,820 --> 00:25:43,580
Mother, you must watch over him.

362
00:25:43,580 --> 00:25:45,560
Bless him so that he'll be safe.

363
00:25:45,560 --> 00:25:47,660
Be safe and sound.

364
00:25:52,879 --> 00:25:57,479
With so many courtyards in the residence, why did she pick this one?

365
00:25:58,199 --> 00:26:00,760
Isn't this too shabby?

366
00:26:00,760 --> 00:26:04,099
This won't work. I must move them to a better place.

367
00:26:08,100 --> 00:26:11,980
Qi, I was looking for you.

368
00:26:11,980 --> 00:26:14,840
- Listen, I... 
 - I was looking for you, too.

369
00:26:14,840 --> 00:26:17,279
What is it? You can tell me.

370
00:26:17,279 --> 00:26:19,698
I want that Qinghe sprig from the dispensary.

371
00:26:19,699 --> 00:26:22,819
What did you say? You little rascal. You...

372
00:26:26,299 --> 00:26:31,498
Well, Qi. You have to know that Qinghe sprig is very valuable.

373
00:26:31,499 --> 00:26:34,418
It's a life-saving medicinal herb. Choose something else.

374
00:26:34,418 --> 00:26:36,738
- I'll surely satisfy your request. 
 - I only want the Qinghe sprig.

375
00:26:36,738 --> 00:26:38,579
I need it urgently.

376
00:26:40,100 --> 00:26:41,500
I can't...

377
00:26:45,299 --> 00:26:47,919
I know what you're worried about.

378
00:26:47,919 --> 00:26:49,298
Don't worry.

379
00:26:49,299 --> 00:26:53,620
With me around, what Zhuang Wenfeng has done won't implicate you.

380
00:26:54,860 --> 00:26:58,180
Can you really handle it?

381
00:26:58,180 --> 00:26:59,980
Of course.

382
00:26:59,980 --> 00:27:02,199
I may be merely a sixth-rank official.

383
00:27:02,199 --> 00:27:05,999
But currently, I'm working for First Prince.

384
00:27:05,999 --> 00:27:10,540
The successful relief efforts in Jiangnan are thanks to First Prince.

385
00:27:10,540 --> 00:27:13,919
After we return, we will definitely be generously...

386
00:27:15,100 --> 00:27:17,119
You're right.

387
00:27:17,119 --> 00:27:19,899
The Qinghe sprig is now yours.

388
00:27:27,820 --> 00:27:30,719
- Did you manage to get the medicinal herb? 
 - It's being decocted.

389
00:27:51,799 --> 00:27:53,599
Is he all right now?

390
00:27:54,459 --> 00:27:56,339
He's safe for now.

391
00:27:59,639 --> 00:28:04,999
I wonder how the First Prince's interrogation of Zhuang Wenfeng is going.

392
00:28:04,999 --> 00:28:08,779
By the way, there are some ledgers in the hidden compartment of Zhuang Wenfeng's side courtyard.

393
00:28:08,779 --> 00:28:12,139
- You must find them. 
 - All right. You can leave it to me.

394
00:28:17,480 --> 00:28:19,080
What's the matter?

395
00:28:20,580 --> 00:28:23,620
You seem different now.

396
00:28:24,720 --> 00:28:26,399
Why are you so nagging?

397
00:28:26,399 --> 00:28:28,219
Do you want me to go or not?

398
00:28:28,219 --> 00:28:31,498
Of course. Only you can handle it, Hero Zhijian.

399
00:28:31,499 --> 00:28:33,099
Off you go now.

400
00:28:34,299 --> 00:28:35,899
Who's there?

401
00:28:37,480 --> 00:28:39,280
 Who are you? 

402
00:28:42,340 --> 00:28:46,538
- What's the matter? 
 - Qi. Qi, what's wrong with this person?

403
00:28:46,538 --> 00:28:49,018
He appeared out of nowhere and gave me a fright.

404
00:28:49,019 --> 00:28:51,079
I didn't lay a finger on him.

405
00:28:51,079 --> 00:28:52,599
I know.

406
00:28:53,680 --> 00:28:55,319
What were you doing hiding outside?

407
00:28:55,319 --> 00:28:58,499
I... I wasn't doing anything.

408
00:28:58,499 --> 00:29:01,161
- He was eavesdropping. 
 - Eavesdropping?

409
00:29:01,161 --> 00:29:04,219
Oh, no, no, no. How could I be eavesdropping?

410
00:29:05,659 --> 00:29:08,839
I only wanted to give you some advice.

411
00:29:08,839 --> 00:29:10,940
Advice for what?

412
00:29:10,940 --> 00:29:14,958
Qi, you may not admit it. But I understand.

413
00:29:14,958 --> 00:29:18,439
Isn't it about choosing a man? It's no big deal.

414
00:29:18,439 --> 00:29:21,379
But let me tell you. You have a bright future ahead.

415
00:29:21,380 --> 00:29:25,600
So you must choose the people around you carefully.

416
00:29:25,620 --> 00:29:28,039
Look at that lad behind you. You can never choose him.

417
00:29:28,039 --> 00:29:30,418
- I beg your pardon. 
 - Listen.

418
00:29:30,418 --> 00:29:32,820
- He has a bad temper. 
 - Ignore him.

419
00:29:34,359 --> 00:29:37,159
Don't take it to heart. He's talking nonsense.

420
00:29:39,380 --> 00:29:40,819
Qi, listen to me.

421
00:29:40,820 --> 00:29:43,739
I'm not done talking, Qi.

422
00:29:48,459 --> 00:29:51,200
Qi, I'm experienced.

423
00:29:51,200 --> 00:29:55,719
A person's character is crucial. And...

424
00:29:58,779 --> 00:30:02,898
Also, you must make the decision in the household.

425
00:30:02,898 --> 00:30:04,980
Rules must not be disregarded.

426
00:30:04,980 --> 00:30:06,738
So, tell me.

427
00:30:06,739 --> 00:30:10,779
Which one did you choose?

428
00:30:10,779 --> 00:30:12,419
   

429
00:30:12,420 --> 00:30:15,258
Your Highness, I'm innocent.

430
00:30:15,259 --> 00:30:19,440
I wouldn't dare to switch the grain distributed by the court.

431
00:30:19,440 --> 00:30:21,018
Someone must have framed me.

432
00:30:21,019 --> 00:30:23,860
Please make a fair judgment for me.

433
00:30:27,419 --> 00:30:31,380
Butler Zhou. He must have done it behind my back.

434
00:30:31,380 --> 00:30:33,900
Butler Zhou is a mere servant.

435
00:30:33,900 --> 00:30:38,180
Without your permission, how would he dare to switch disaster relief grain?

436
00:30:38,180 --> 00:30:44,100
Besides, this is only a portion of the official grain.

437
00:30:44,100 --> 00:30:46,240
Where is the rest?

438
00:30:46,240 --> 00:30:48,339
Fess up now.

439
00:30:48,340 --> 00:30:52,340
Your Highness, I'm telling the truth.

440
00:30:52,340 --> 00:30:56,099
You... You may be a high-ranking noble.

441
00:30:56,099 --> 00:30:59,080
But I am an appointed official of the court.

442
00:30:59,080 --> 00:31:02,879
You surely can't force a confession from me.

443
00:31:02,879 --> 00:31:05,020
Outrageous!

444
00:31:09,779 --> 00:31:11,379
 By the way, 

445
00:31:11,380 --> 00:31:13,778
 Official Mu wants me to remind Your Highness one thing. 

446
00:31:13,779 --> 00:31:17,399
 Zhuang Wenfeng may have no guts. But he's cunning. 

447
00:31:17,400 --> 00:31:21,418
 She hopes that you won't act impulsively to avoid falling for his tricks. 

448
00:31:23,499 --> 00:31:25,099
Fine.

449
00:31:26,079 --> 00:31:29,540
Since you said you were framed,

450
00:31:29,540 --> 00:31:32,799
follow me back to the capital

451
00:31:32,799 --> 00:31:35,420
so that the law can seek justice for you.

452
00:31:37,259 --> 00:31:39,538
Your Highness. Your Highness! Your Highness!

453
00:31:39,539 --> 00:31:41,819
Your Highness! I'm innocent, Your Highness!

454
00:31:41,820 --> 00:31:43,218
Your Highness, please! Let me explain, Your Highness!

455
00:31:43,219 --> 00:31:46,060
I'm innocent, Your Highness!

456
00:31:47,380 --> 00:31:50,679
 These may be old injuries. But you still need to be careful. 

457
00:31:56,979 --> 00:31:58,679
Thank you.

458
00:32:00,240 --> 00:32:02,040
Don't mention it.

459
00:32:04,760 --> 00:32:07,000
You've been nice to Juli, after all.

460
00:32:09,019 --> 00:32:11,819
Juli always talks about food.

461
00:32:11,820 --> 00:32:15,140
Other than that, you're the one she talks about the most.

462
00:32:18,459 --> 00:32:20,639
You must not mistreat Juli.

463
00:32:20,639 --> 00:32:22,139
Do you hear me?

464
00:32:22,140 --> 00:32:24,040
I won't.

465
00:32:24,040 --> 00:32:25,579
I'm glad to hear that.

466
00:32:28,620 --> 00:32:31,140
Is this where you two lived?

467
00:32:34,120 --> 00:32:40,920
Yes. My father has many concubines.

468
00:32:40,920 --> 00:32:47,399
We're lucky to have a place to stay and enough to eat and wear.

469
00:32:48,480 --> 00:32:51,780
Juli used to be picked on in other places.

470
00:32:51,780 --> 00:32:54,799
She doesn't eat a lot because she's greedy.

471
00:32:54,799 --> 00:32:59,000
But if she doesn't eat, there won't be anything for her.

472
00:33:06,779 --> 00:33:09,760
 - Are you hungry? 
   

473
00:33:16,499 --> 00:33:19,980
 I'm going out for a while. Can you keep a lookout for me? 

474
00:33:49,580 --> 00:33:51,018
 Thank you, Juli. 

475
00:33:51,019 --> 00:33:52,899
 Did you finish your steamed bun? 

476
00:33:52,899 --> 00:33:55,319
 I'll get you more next time. 

477
00:33:56,860 --> 00:33:58,860
 I'll get going first. 

478
00:34:02,219 --> 00:34:05,379
The older maid found out about Juli keeping a lookout for me.

479
00:34:05,380 --> 00:34:08,460
She'd rather get punished than reveal my secret.

480
00:34:08,460 --> 00:34:09,819
What happened after that?

481
00:34:09,820 --> 00:34:16,040
Later, I begged my mother to talk to First Madam to let Juli come to us.

482
00:34:17,539 --> 00:34:24,060
That's how Juli became the closest person to me besides my mother.

483
00:34:26,780 --> 00:34:32,680
At that time, my mother forced me to take lessons with Tutor Shang every day.

484
00:34:33,340 --> 00:34:35,658
At first, I thought First Madam was indifferent to us

485
00:34:35,659 --> 00:34:41,039
because she thought nothing useful would come out of this shabby courtyard.

486
00:34:41,039 --> 00:34:46,179
But when I think about it, she even agreed to assign Juli to our courtyard.

487
00:34:46,220 --> 00:34:48,219
It shows how smart and capable she is.

488
00:34:48,220 --> 00:34:53,360
Anything happening in this family cannot be hidden from her.

489
00:34:56,780 --> 00:34:59,840
First Madam's situation was similar to my mother's at first.

490
00:34:59,840 --> 00:35:02,219
She thought she found a good husband.

491
00:35:02,220 --> 00:35:06,359
So she brought a huge dowry and married my father.

492
00:35:06,359 --> 00:35:09,360
It gave my father the capital to start his business.

493
00:35:14,019 --> 00:35:18,980
But who would have thought that this man

494
00:35:18,980 --> 00:35:21,760
would fancy other women?

495
00:35:21,760 --> 00:35:25,240
He married them one by one

496
00:35:25,240 --> 00:35:26,699
and brought them home.

497
00:35:26,700 --> 00:35:30,879
Once they got here, he would neglect them.

498
00:35:32,220 --> 00:35:36,900
Yet, how many women can be like First Madam,

499
00:35:36,900 --> 00:35:39,579
who can make their own decisions?

500
00:35:44,179 --> 00:35:49,760
But my mother had it better than Miss Song and the others.

501
00:35:54,800 --> 00:35:56,760
Look at that portrait.

502
00:35:57,759 --> 00:35:59,560
That's my mother.

503
00:36:01,340 --> 00:36:05,180
Doesn't she look beautiful when she smiles?

504
00:36:07,780 --> 00:36:10,079
Everyone says,

505
00:36:10,099 --> 00:36:14,859
"A single glance and smile can captivate the entire city."

506
00:36:14,860 --> 00:36:17,259
That's how her name came about.

507
00:36:24,880 --> 00:36:26,680
My Lord?

508
00:36:26,680 --> 00:36:29,300
My Lord, you're awake.

509
00:36:30,139 --> 00:36:32,500
My Lord, you're finally awake.

510
00:36:32,500 --> 00:36:34,159
How do you feel?

511
00:36:37,260 --> 00:36:41,660
I just dreamed of you.

